This document discussed the underlying ideas about the structure of the app, the layout and the variety of options it will contain for smooth
and efficient costumer experience.

#Structure 

Simple single page interface.
Sticky Notes UI.
Different set of colors for notes window.

Options : Create, Edit, Delete, Save, Archive.


#Content

Content is text only !!

Standard fonts.
Option of bold, italics can be given.
Layout should be small, if content is more, the layout should be scrollable.
